org.xbib.elasticsearch.gatherer
Enum ControlKeys

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<ControlKeys>
      org.xbib.elasticsearch.gatherer.ControlKeys
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ControlKeys>
public enum ControlKeys
extends Enum<ControlKeys>

The names of keys with a special meaning for controlling Elasticsearch indexing. Mostly, they map to the Elasticsearch bulk item control keys. The _job column denotes an ID for the event of a fetch execution.
